# WorkflowType

The type of the workflow. Currently the only valid value is 'Workflow::Setup'. 

## Enum

* `WORKFLOW_COLON_COLON_SETUP` (value: `'Workflow::Setup'`)

* `WORKFLOW_COLON_COLON_INSTANCE` (value: `'Workflow::Instance'`)
